## Security

DBPA implements several security measures:

- Query sanitization
- Input validation
- Access control
- Secure credential management
- Audit logging

See our [Security Guide](docs/security.md) for details.

## Testing

Run the test suite:

```bash
# Unit tests
pytest tests/unit

# Integration tests
robot tests/robot/tests

# Coverage report
pytest --cov=dbpa
```

